title: Siouxsie & The Banshees - 1981 - Once Upon a Time: The Singles [
description:
Once Upon a Time: The Singles is Siouxsie & the Banshees's 1981 compilation album featuring the band's U.K. single releases to date. The album featured several songs that had been released as singles yet had not appeared on any of the Banshees' four albums.

In 2002, Q Magazine named Once Upon A Time: The Singles the 7th Greatest Album of All-Time by a Female Artist.

Track Listing
1 - Hong Kong Garden
2 - Mirage
3 - The Staircase (Mystery)
4 - Playground Twist
5 - Love in a Void
6 - Happy House
